Class Receipt

Object
Receipt
public class Receipt extends Object
Represents a receipt for a successful BTO flat booking. Contains details about the applicant and the booked flat.
Since:
2025-03-16
Version:
1.0
Author:
SC2002 G Team

      receiptId - The unique identifier for this receipt

      applicantAge - The age of the applicant
      maritalStatus - The marital status of the applicant
      flatTypeBooked - The type of flat booked
